<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 5 - 8. Paratype of Manipuria yuae sp. nov., female 5 habitus, dorsal view 6 habitus, ventral view 7 female genitalia and reproductive organs, dorsal view 8 genitalia and reproductive organs, ventral view. Abbreviations: Sg spiculum gastrale; S 8 sternite 8; S 9 sternite 9; T 8 tergite 8; T 9 tergite 9; Sp D spermathecal duct; Sp spermatheca." , "Figures 21 - 23. Sclerites in internal sac 21 holotype of Manipuria yuae 22 paratype of M. yuae from Yunnan 23 M. dohertyi from Yunnan A lateral view B dorsal view C ventral view." , "Figures 15 - 20. Aedeagus and internal sac of Manipuria spp. 15 holotype of M. yuae sp. nov., lateral view 16 paratype of M. yuae from Yunnan, lateral view 17 M. dohertyi from Yunnan, lateral view 18 holotype of M. yuae sp. nov., dorsal view 19 paratype of M. yuae sp. nov. from Yunnan in dorsal view 20 M. dohertyi from Yunnan, dorsal view. Abbreviations: DS dorsal sclerite; MS dorsal sclerite; VS dorsal sclerite; IS internal sac; ML median lobe; SCM second connecting membrane; T tegmen." , "Figures 1 - 4. Manipuria spp. 1 holotype of M. yuae sp. nov., dorsal view 2 holotype of M. yuae sp. nov., ventral view 3 head of holotype of M. yuae sp. nov., ventro-lateral view 4 head of M. dohertyi, male, ventro-lateral view." , "Figures 9, 10. Manipuria yuae sp. nov. 9 head, dorsal view 10 spermatheca and spermathecal gland." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/493759" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/493761" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/493757" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/493762" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/493758" .

